  "design_notes": "Hard chart tailored to the rhythmic density of the electronic synth leads and percussion. The intro presents a high-energy stream of steps, integrating light 16th-note syncopation. A running-man pattern takes over during the vocal-esque synth hooks. The drop and bridge incorporate tight drills and jumpstream textures, with carefully calculated holds matching the sustained synths. A short breather section is placed at the very end to match the outro fade.",
